summary: Spent last hour reading theories about Miles in mcu (bc i want him so much like cmon it will be great) and some other info and...
body:
Spent last hour reading theories about Miles in mcu (bc i want him so much like cmon it will be great) and some other info and yes, I’m confused about the fact that Peter and Ned look alike Miles and Ganke and something like that, but I don’t see a promblem there

I see promblem in a fact, that 42 spider was from Oscorp (like peter’s spider), but we don’t have oscorp in mcu (yet). I don’t know about Marvel and Sony’s rules for Osborns, and marvel didn’t show from where Peter get his power (bc “everyone already knew it”), but I don’t remember any of oscorp mentions in mcu actually (mb I’m wrong lmao)

So, if Miles will be in mcu (he will be 100%) It would be better for them to explain about spiders, oscorp and etc. i may be wrong, but it’s a big deal for me

And yeah, i wabt harry in mcu too, fucking fangirl
